OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,FHome Alone 2 and My Left Foot actress
OL,7,FBrenda Fricker, who became the first
OL,8,Fwoman from the Republic of Ireland to
OL,9,Fwin an Oscar, has died aged 81.
OL,11,FHer death was confirmed by her agent
OL,12,FPhil Belfield, who described the Irish
OL,13,Factress as a "legend" whom he was
OL,14,F"honoured to know".
OL,16,FBelfield's statement said: "It is with
OL,17,Fmuch sadness that I share the news
OL,18,Fthat beloved actress Brenda Fricker
OL,19,Fpassed away last night peacefully
OL,20,Fafter a period of ill health, at the
OL,21,Fage of 81."
OL,26,@uD@NOUuD@UO]vD@AOUvD@RO]xD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
