OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784395090
OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,FHe had: "We will never see her like
OL,7,Fagain and the world is lesser for the
OL,8,Flack of her. I was honoured to know,
OL,9,Flove and work with her and she will
OL,10,Falways have a place in my heart and in
OL,11,Fthe heart of so many film and TV fans
OL,12,Fthe world over."
OL,14,FFricker won the Best Supporting
OL,15,FActress Oscar for her performance as
OL,16,FBridget Fagan Brown in 1989's My Left
OL,17,FFoot, which tells the story of an
OL,18,FIrish man named Christy Brown who was
OL,19,Fborn with cerebral palsy and could
OL,20,Fcontrol only his left foot.
OL,26,@nD@IOU
