OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,FShe was also well known for her role
OL,7,Fin the 1992 follow-up to Home Alone,
OL,8,Fwhere she played Pigeon Lady, a
OL,9,Fhomeless woman in New York's Central
OL,10,FPark.
OL,12,FThe Irish premier Micheal Martin has
OL,13,Fsaid he is "deeply saddened" to learn
OL,14,Fof the death of Brenda Fricker.
OL,16,FIn a post on the social media site X,
OL,17,Fthe Taoiseach said: "She was an iconic
OL,18,Ffigure in Irish film and theatre, an
OL,19,FOscar winner and an actor of world
OL,20,Frenown.
OL,26,@tD@XrpuD@LOUuD@\O]yD@UOU
