OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784395090
OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,F"My thoughts are with her family and
OL,7,Ffriends."
OL,9,FIrish Tanaiste Simon Harris said he
OL,10,Fwas "deeply saddened" to learn of
OL,11,FFricker's death, describing her as a
OL,12,F"national treasure" and extending his
OL,13,F"deepest sympathies" to her family and
OL,14,Ffriends.
OL,16,FHe added: "As the first Irish woman to
OL,17,Fwin an acting Oscar, she opened doors
OL,18,Fand set a standard of excellence that
OL,19,Fcontinues to inspire generations of
OL,20,FIrish artists.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@IO]qD@HrprD@EOUrD@UO]tD@AOUtD@
OL,26,ASO]uD@AOUuD@TO]xD@KOU
