OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784395090
OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,F"She was a consummate performer who
OL,7,Fgraced our screens and stages with
OL,8,Fremarkable talent and authenticity.
OL,9,FBrenda brought depth and humanity to
OL,10,Fevery role she undertook.
OL,12,FFricker was also part of the original
OL,13,Fcast of BBC medical drama Casualty and
OL,14,Ffeatured alongside Cate Blanchett in
OL,15,FVeronica Guerin (2003), as well as
OL,16,Fappearing in ITV drama Upstairs,
OL,17,FDownstairs and soap opera Coronation
OL,18,FStreet.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
