OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe was also well known for roles in
OL,12,Ffilms such as So I Married An Axe
OL,13,FMurderer (1993), Angels In The
OL,14,FOutfield (1994), and A Time To Kill
OL,15,F(1996).
OL,17,FHer later roles included the TV
OL,18,Fadaptation of Graham Norton's first
OL,19,Fnovel Holding, directed by Kathy
OL,20,FBurke, and the Channel 5 drama series
OL,21,FThe Catch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
