OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784395090
OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,FFricker also made numerous stage
OL,7,Fappearances in plays such as Lavender
OL,8,FBlue and A Pagan's Place at theatres
OL,9,Fincluding the National Theatre and
OL,10,FRoyal Court Theatre.
OL,12,FBelfield said "Brenda's versatility
OL,13,Fwas renowned" and that her most recent
OL,14,Fsolo film performance in Tadhg
OL,15,FO'Sullivan's The Swallow showed "the
OL,16,Ftruth and majesty of Brenda as an
OL,17,Factor" and said it was "a thing of
OL,18,Fbeauty".
OL,26,@tD@OOUuD@MO]wD@aOUyD@FO]yD@XOUzD@GO]
