OL,3,CBrenda Fricker, Oscar-winning My Left
OL,4,CFoot actress, dies aged 81
OL,6,FFricker's memoir She Died Young
OL,7,Fappeared on the Irish Sunday Times
OL,8,Fbestseller list, and she was recently
OL,9,Fgranted the Freedom of the City of
OL,10,FDublin, which Belfield said she was
OL,11,F"particularly thrilled and proud of".
OL,13,FShe was married to director Barry
OL,14,FDavies from 1979 until their divorce
OL,15,Fin 1988.
